These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, billiard
House: colonial, art-deco, gothic-revival
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, old-henry
1. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the colonial house##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
5. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Game   | billiard       | bridge     | whist    |
| House   | gothic-revival   | art-deco          | colonial   |
| Cigar         | fonseca | old-henry | game |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, thai, brazilian
3 different games are played: canasta, go, monopoly
House: townhouse, ranch-style, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is the brazilian##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
3. the brazilian is on the left of the thai##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
6. the futuristic house is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality    | argentine     | brazilian  | thai  |
| Game   | monopoly | go | canasta    |
| House     | townhouse      | futuristic    | ranch-style |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, airplane
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, russian
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, mauve, lavender
1. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes lavender is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the russian is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the russian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Transport          | scooter         | airplane     | skateboard   |
| Nationality   | malaysian       | canadian     | russian |
| Color         | lavender | turquise | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, havana, bluemaster
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, dutch, brazilian
City: berlin, paris, new-york
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the italian is in an odd position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the dutch is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Cigar   | alhambra | bluemaster  | havana |
| Nationality        | brazilian | dutch  | italian |
| City        | berlin | paris | new-york         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
City: venice, nizza, new-york
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, airplane
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, july
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| City   | new-york | venice  | nizza  |
| Transport   | trike  | jet-ski | airplane |
| Birthday           | june  | july    | april    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, software-developer
3 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, turtle
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, july, december
1. the coach is between the person who's birthday is in december and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the owner of the mouse is the electrician##1
3. the coach is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Job    | software-developer  | coach  | electrician        |
| Pet       | turtle | cat | mouse |
| Birthday   | november    | july   | december   |

