.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, drawing, traveling
There 3 different types of food: plum, tomato, cranberry
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person eating plum and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | drawing        | traveling |
| Food           | plum   | tomato      | cranberry     |
| Beverage         | juice | lemonade | hot-chocolate    |

