.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, metal, house
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall, game
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of house##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
5. the game-smoker is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Music-Genre    | disco   | metal | house       |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate  | coffee  | fanta |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | aristoff  | game       |

