.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, handball
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, metal
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person driving the subway and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Sport         | swimming | biathlon | handball |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | funk  | dubstep     |
| Transport           | skateboard     | snowmobile     | subway          |

