.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: grapes, kale, garlic
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, singing
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the person eating kale is the person eating kale##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
6. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | milk        | fanta   |
| Food   | kale | garlic | grapes    |
| Hobby   | singing         | puzzles      | chess |

