.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-11::.
City: london, venice, liverpool
3 different games are played: domino, poker, canasta
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, potato
1. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing domino##1
2. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| City         | liverpool | venice      | london  |
| Game         | domino         | canasta      | poker    |
| Food   | asparagus         | potato | avocado |

