.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, d&b, dubstep
City: hamburg, rome, prague
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, july
1. the person traveling to rome is the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to prague is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Music-Genre         | d&b        | blues  | dubstep      |
| City           | prague | hamburg | rome |
| Birthday   | september        | january   | july  |

