.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, family
House: craftsman, art-deco, cape-cod
City: rome, berlin, miami
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | adventure | thriller | family |
| House           | craftsman | cape-cod   | art-deco  |
| City   | berlin | rome   | miami        |

