.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, rose
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, blood-red, brown
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, ice-hockey
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who likes azure is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Flower   | daisy      | rose | zinnia |
| Color   | blood-red        | azure         | brown |
| Sport           | rugby | ice-hockey         | snowboarding   |

