1. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
3. the person eating radish is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Food         | banana   | pear     | radish   |
| Cigar           | siglo  | aristoff | davidoff |
| Transport   | ship | skateboard     | scooter |

