The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, hiking, woodworking
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Cigar     | aristoff      | dannemann | swisher |
| Hobby     | hiking | writing      | woodworking           |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker  | scrabble    |

