.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: poker, go, bridge
House: ranch-style, art-deco, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, may
1. the person playing go is between the person playing poker and the art-deco house##2
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
7. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game         | bridge      | go | poker |
| House   | art-deco | ranch-style      | cape-cod    |
| Birthday           | may      | february        | october       |

 